### 1. Create an order (dynamic - fetches real product price & details)
POST {{baseUrl}}/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "items": [
        {
            "productId": "{{productId}}",
            "quantity": 2
        }
    ],
    "shippingAddress": {
        "street": "123 Main Street",
        "city": "New York",
        "state": "NY",
        "zipCode": "10001",
        "country": "USA"
    }
}

